Pre-release fixes

commit.message: Addressing PR feedback
Skip getting credentials if the endpoint is public and is not the upload API
Extra error handling when unable to find credential provider
Environment variable to disable the credential provider's interactive mode
Checking credentials are valid and calling the cred provider with IsRetry=true in case they aren't
Fixing unit tests after change in keyring that made the keyring chainer a normal backend. Also slightly lowering the priority of artifacts-keyring so the chainer can win in priority
Bumping version to latest that worked on multiple platforms
Reading all stderr first, which may contain instructions from the credential provider for Device Flow authentication.
Getting result as bytes and handling decoding errors
Supporting old and test URLs
Calling the credential provider in non-plugin mode and updating the version used; the latest version can return the credentials in JSON format.
